  "texts": [
    "Its purpose is to inform individuals about their current ability levels and provide them with guidelines to enhance their knowledge for improved future learning outcomes (Boud & Molloy, 2013).",
    "Feedback contributes to students' understanding of their performance by operating on multiple levels as follows (Hattie & Timperley, 2007):1.",
    "The task level involves guiding students on specific actions needed to arrive at the correct answer.2.",
    "The process level informs students about the thought processes required to approach tasks correctly.3.",
    "The self-regulated learning (SRL) level pertains to students' ability to monitor and guide themselves toward achieving their learning objectives. 4."
  ],
